DTSTART:20260418T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join a restoration work party at East Duwamish GS: S Chicago St
	. \\nHelp take care of the forest along this neighborhood trail! Depending
	 on the time of the year\\\, we’ll be pulling and removing ivy\\\, cutting
	 back and digging out blackberry or planting new plants\; and always havin
