UID:0jXy2bXM8czIn44tJTivH
SUMMARY:Executive Council (EC) Meeting
DTSTAMP:20260413T050911Z
DTSTART:20260421T154500Z
DESCRIPTION:Location Type: Online Event sponsors: UW Bothell General Facult
	y Organization Accessibility Contact: dawn3@uw.edu\n\nIf you would like to
	 attend\, please email Dawn Moncalieri\, GFO Progr am Coordinator\, at  da
	wn3@uw.edu to request the zoom link.\n\n\\*\\*\\*AN AGENDA WILL BE ADDED H
	ERE ONE WEEK PRIOR TO MEETING\\*\\*\\*\n\nThe Executive Council is an elec
	ted faculty council of the GFO. Its responsibilities are to advise the Cha
	nce llor and Vice Chancellors on matters involving academic policy\, polic
	y regarding faculty promotion and tenure\; and the development and impleme
	ntation of the campus vision statement\, and on the general welfare of the
	 campus.\n\nEC meetings occur every other Tuesday\, 8:45-10 :45am. To lear
