SUMMARY:Mercer Island Chamber Sustainable Fashion Show
DTSTAMP:20260413T050911Z
DTSTART:20260423T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Sustainable Style Hits the Runway! Join us for the Chamber’s Fi
	rst Sustainable Fashion Show—where style meets purpose. Featuring Mercer I
	sland's own thrift store and local consignment boutiques\, eco-friendly ac
	cessories\, and fashion-forward products that support sustainability. Feat
