	nEvent Details \n\n When: The last Friday of each month\n\n Time: 11 am to
	 1 pm\n\n Where: Labateyah Youth Home\, 9010 13th Ave NW\, Seattle\, WA 98
	117\n\nUpcoming Workshop Topics \n\n March 27: Veterans Benefits Administr
	ation 101 \\(Disability Compensation\, Education\, Home Loans\, Burials\, 
	& more\\)\n\n April 24: Veterans Health Administration 101 \\(VA Hospital 
	& Medical Care\\)\n\n May 29: Veteran Service Officer Networking & Additio
	nal Benefits 101\n\nWhat to Expect \n\n Lunch provided for attendees\n\n G
	ift cards available for veterans\, veteran spouses\, or caretakers of vete
	rans \\(Limit 1 per household\\)\n\n Transportation is available\, if need
	ed\n\n Registration is encouraged to help us prepare: https://forms.office
	.com/r/KrRTQ86ZPr \n\n  \n\nQuestions? Please email us at veterans@unitedi
	ndians.org \n\nNote: Workshop topics and schedules are subject to change. 
