DTSTAMP:20260413T050911Z
DTSTART:20260426T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:The Arboretum's beloved Spring Plant Sale returns to the Graham
	 Visitors Center on Sunday\, April 26\, from 10am to 2pm.\n\nIt features a
	 unique selection of perennials\, shrubs\, ground covers\, and young trees
	\, including plants propagated from the Arboretum's prized collections.\n\
	nThis year's event will also celebrate Earth Week with live music\, free h
	orticultural demonstrations\, nature education activities\, and community 
	tabling. Learn how to make your own mushroom kit\, sharpen your gardening 
	tools\, and more!\n\nAll sales support tree care\, science education\, and
	 volunteerism at the Arboretum.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/d
	etails/arboretum-spring-plant-sale/18543773/2026-04-26T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday
